summary: This document is a secure message from TD Ameritrade regarding a transfer request made by Jeffrey. It confirms the receipt of the transfer request and informs him that it has been forwarded to the processing team for review. The message also provides contact information for further inquiries.

persons.name: Jeffrey
persons.context: Jeffrey is the client who submitted a transfer request to TD Ameritrade.

persons.name: David Redlinger
persons.context: David Redlinger is the representative from TD Ameritrade who communicated with Jeffrey regarding the transfer request.

events.title: Transfer Request Submitted
events.description: Jeffrey submitted a transfer request to TD Ameritrade for processing.

keyFacts: The transfer request was submitted by Jeffrey to TD Ameritrade.
The request involves a partial transfer to Deutsche Bank.
David Redlinger is the representative who acknowledged the receipt of the transfer request.
